data.enText: to clean sth using a substance that kills bacteria

data.chText: 给表面 / 房间 / 伤口消毒
消除（计算机）病毒； 给（电脑）杀毒
data.enText: to run a computer program to get rid of a computer virus

tr: destroy microorganisms or pathogens by cleansing

value.def: If you disinfect something, you clean it using a substance that kills germs.

example.ex: Chlorine is used to disinfect water...
Make sure the draining board, sink and plug hole are regularly disinfected.
example.tran: 滴水板、水槽和塞孔一定要定期消毒。
